column5: Great markings and colour on that fish....what a beauty!!  I'm still lookin' for a pike in the 40's.....
Thats a good one. Congrats on a nice looking fatty.
Caught a nice 41incher this morning at the south end of cooks, my first pike over 40, she swam away just fine
Awesome Gator hope to get a bunch like that in the fall .
sweet....ive only caught fish that big in the ocean
Nice fish LF! Congrats on the PB!
Thanks to all, can't wait for the next milestone, 45
Nice fish!!! Were you trolling or casting? I was up at Dalrymple yesterday and your pike could eat the ones I caught! Scooter
Thats a real nice looking fish there LefroyFisherman. Grats
Sweet now that's got some nice colors to it Congrats SBK
Awesome Dude! glad I was there to witness this beauty..
Congrats on a great fish!  Good luck on the 45"er!
Awesome pike!! What did you get it on?
